      <p><strong>At Sage Street, we work hard to bring you unique, handcrafted blends that'll wow you every time.</strong></p>
      <p>With our organic, fair-trade coffee beans, we brew our orders one by one so that your cup is custom tailored just for you. Our coffee is filled with love, and we hope you'll taste it too.</p>
      <div class="about__img">
