      <p><strong>Our story begins like this...</strong><p>
      <p>At the tender age of 16, Mary Chang found the perfect cup of coffee at a tiny roadside coffee shop in Taiwan--it was love at first sip. From then on, Mary fell down the rabbit-hole, becoming enamored with coffee and all of its variations. In college, she embarked on trips all around the country, taste-testing brews from all around the world in hopes of finding the perfect brews. She decided to bring these experiences home to share, incorporating all the flavors of her travels into a few key blends that offered only the boldest, smoothest, and most complex
      flavors. <br />
      These original blends led the way to the opening of the first Sage
      Street location in Portland in 2012. Today, our stores continue to grow, and we hope to continue bringing you only the best coffee we can offer.
      </p>
